high_descs: Go across the room  to the coffee maker, turn to the right.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter to the left of the gray plate.
Turn to the right, go across the room to the fridge that is on the left.
Cut the potato that is inside the fridge into slices and close the door.
Back up from the fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge in front of the potato.
Move up closer to the fridge.
Remove a slice of potato from the fridge.
Turn around, go forward, hang a right and go to the microwave that is across the room.
Put the potato inside the microwave, turn it on to cook, remove the cooked potato from the microwave when it is done.
Turn around, go across the room to the wall, hang a left and go to the fridge.
Put the cooked slice of potato inside the fridge on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked potato inside the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the countertop left of the toaster
Pick up the farther knife
Go to the fridge
Cut the potato in the fridge
Close the fridge
Open the fridge and put the knife in
Close the fridge
Open the fridge and take a potato slice
Go to the microwave
Heat the potato slice
Go to the fridge
Put the potato slice in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked potato slice and a butterknife in the fridge

high_descs: Walk across the room and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Turn right, walk across the room and turn left to face the fridge.
Cut the potato in the fridge into slices.
Look down to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge in front of the sliced potato.
Look down to stand facing the fridge.
Pick up a slice of potato from in the fridge.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the microwave over the stove.
Heat the potato in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left to face the fridge.
Place the potato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of potato and then store in the fridge.
